section.section:
After considering the recommendations of the Maryland Optometric Association and the Maryland Society of Eye Physicians and Surgeons, the Secretary shall adopt regulations that establish:
Standards of quality for therapeutically certified optometrists and optometric care;
An ongoing quality assurance program that includes the monitoring and study of the joint management of primary open-angle glaucoma patients under § 11-404.2(c) of this subtitle;
A program to evaluate the cost of optometric care; and
A plan to monitor complaint investigation.
